name: Comfy, quite room with all you need.
description:
My place is near public transportation, very bikeable, very walkable and surrounded with green areas where you can enjoy a good time relaxing and exercising. You can get to any destination in just minutes: MGH and Longwood Medical Area (Beth Israel, Dana Farber, Children's Hospital) in about 15-20 minutes, Boston Medical Center in about 5 to 10 minutes, Tufts University and Downtown Boston in about 15 to 20 minutes.
There are two gyms near by, a Walgreen's Pharmacy and the South Bay Mall.
